1.1.name: wordpress/starred-review
1.1.description:
A WordPress plugin that will allow you to post reviews to your website. The plugin is inspired by Kottke's movie reviews. It allows you to rate different things and place them in different categories. This is a basic plugin and won't hold actual written reviews, but will allow you to link to reviews you may have posted and link to product pages. It's the plugin I use for my reviews section/page.

The changelog is a good place to start if you want to know what has changed since you last downloaded the plugin.
